name: WKExtendedRuntimeSessionErrorCode
desc: The error codes reported by extended runtime sessions.

items.name: case scheduledTooFarInAdvance
items.desc: The app attempted to schedule a session too far in the future.

items.name: case mustBeActiveToStartOrSchedule
items.desc: The watchOS app attempted to start or schedule a session while not in an active state.

items.name: case notYetStarted
items.desc: The app invalidated the session before it started.

items.name: case exceededResourceLimits
items.desc: The session exceeded its resource limits.

items.name: case barDisabled
items.desc: The user has disabled background app refresh.

items.name: case notApprovedToStartSession
items.desc: The app attempted to start a session, but doesnâ€™t have a valid session type.

items.name: case notApprovedToSchedule
items.desc: The app attempted to schedule a session, but the session type does not support scheduling.
